## Post-Deploy Checklist

- [ ] Visit `https://voxera2026.in` — verify homepage loads fast
- [ ] Test admin login at `/admin`
- [ ] Test event registration flow end-to-end
- [ ] Submit contact form — verify rate limiting works
- [ ] Check mobile responsiveness
- [ ] Uncomment GA4 in [index.html](file:///c:/Users/chara/Downloads/vzzz13/index.html) → add your `G-XXXXXXXXXX` ID
- [ ] Upload 192×192 and 512×512 icons to `public/icons/` for PWA
- [ ] Run: `npx lighthouse https://voxera2026.in --view`

